    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in 'as-is' condition and requires significant attention. The exterior shows heavy signs of age, including noticeable rust spots on the wheel arches and several deep scratches and dents across the body panels. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and will likely need a comprehensive overhaul; there are also visible fluid leaks. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears in the fabric, and some of the dashboard electronics are non-functional. This is a project car best suited for someone looking for a complete restoration or for use as a parts vehicle.",
      "price": 8500.0,
