    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of distinguished character and proven reliability. This unit has been maintained to a high standard, exhibiting robust mechanical performance and a well-preserved interior. It offers a seamless blend of sophisticated engineering and enduring style, ideal for those who demand consistent excellence in their daily commute. We invite you to experience a vehicle that exemplifies both functional superiority and professional presentation.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! If you're looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been super well-taken care of, you\u2019ve found it! This car has been my pride and joy, and it still runs like a dream. It\u2019s in really solid shape and totally ready for its next adventure. I\u2019ve kept up with the maintenance, so you can just hop in and go. It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a quality vehicle without that brand-new price tag. I'd love for it to go to a good home\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This engine features individual throttle bodies and a recently recalibrated dual-VANOS system, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency across the powerband. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox offers precise engagement, sending torque through a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a cooling system overhaul with a high-flow water pump. The suspension geometry remains true, benefitting from refreshed control arm bushings to maintain toe and camber stability during spirited cornering. While the finish shows minor road-derived character, the mechanical integrity and chassis kinematics are optimized for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained. Ready for immediate sale.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and reliability, having been kept in consistent, road-ready condition. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, with only minor, expected surface imperfections from standard highway use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the premium upholstery shows minimal wear, and all electronic features\u2014including the navigation system, heated seats, and premium audio\u2014are fully operational. Under the hood, the car has been serviced at regular intervals, with a documented history of oil changes and recent fluid flushes. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the braking system is sharp and responsive. It drives straight and quiet, offering a smooth experience for both city commuting and long-distance travel. This is a solid, honest car for a buyer who values mechanical integrity and a well-preserved interior.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, representing a premier acquisition opportunity for the discerning driver. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure mechanical reliability and peak operational performance. Characterized by its robust service history and preserved aesthetic condition, this vehicle offers a sophisticated driving experience and exceptional long-term value. We invite serious inquiries to appreciate the superior engineering and dependable nature of this professional-grade selection.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks great on the road? This car has been well-loved and is in really solid shape. It runs super smoothly and definitely has plenty of life left for its next owner! It\u2019s been my trusty companion, and I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see it go, but it's totally ready for its next adventure. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin or have any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, known for its 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, delivering power to the rear wheels via a limited-slip differential. Technical highlights include a documented Vanos system service and rear subframe reinforcement, addressing the chassis's known stress points. The suspension geometry remains true, offering the tactile feedback and neutral handling characteristic of the M-division's peak engineering. While the exterior shows minor signs of use consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains robust with crisp throttle synchronization and a linear torque curve. It is a turn-key performance machine for the discerning enthusiast who prioritizes mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
